# Snake Game (PyQt5) — Final Polished Edition

A fully polished and modern Snake Game built using **Python + PyQt5**, featuring:
- Start Menu (difficulty selection, high score display)
- Difficulty levels (Easy / Medium / Hard)
- Saving and loading high scores
- Gradient background + grid lines
- Polished UI and snake/food visuals
- Food never spawns inside the snake
- Pause / Resume (P key)
- Game Over screen with restart option
- Fully commented source code for learning + portfolio use
- Smooth grid-based movement  
- Collision detection (walls + self)
- Clean scoring system
- Snake grows as it eats
- Gradient background  
- Grid pattern  
- Different color snake head  
- Circular food  
- Score bar  
- High score saved to `highscore.txt`
- Difficulty-based timer speeds:
  - **Easy:** 200ms  
  - **Medium:** 150ms  
  - **Hard:** 100ms  
pip install PyQt5
